# PDF Layout & Alignment Refinement

This plan addresses visual inconsistencies and overlapping issues in generated PDF reports.

## Proposed Changes

### [MODIFY] [Payslip.jsx](file:///c:/Users/mathi/Desktop/AntiGravity%20Demos/HRMS%20Singapore/client/src/pages/Payslip.jsx)
- Update all `autoTable` calls (Earnings, Deductions, CPF, Employer Contributions, Attendance) to include:
  - `columnStyles: { 0: { cellWidth: 140 }, 1: { cellWidth: 'auto', halign: 'right' } }`
  - This ensures standard "Description" column width and right-aligned "Amount" columns across all sections.

