- **Margins**: Add `margin: { bottom: 30 }` to all `autoTable` calls in [exportSummaryPDF](file:///c:/Users/mathi/Desktop/AntiGravity%20Demos/HRMS%20Singapore/client/src/pages/Leave.jsx#163-232) and [exportIndividualPDF](file:///c:/Users/mathi/Desktop/AntiGravity%20Demos/HRMS%20Singapore/client/src/pages/Leave.jsx#233-337).
